headline: Trane, Autodesk partnership and C.Scale launch cast spotlight on carbon reduction software
summary: Integrating Trane's TRACE software with Autodesk Revit will help engineers and operators optimize HVAC systems, while C.Scale can streamline carbon emission estimates across building lifecycles, the companies said.
